=== Other ===
[[File:Miminashi-sangaku.jpg|thumb|A sangaku dedication]]
*As a remnant of it once being called “Miminashi-yama,” the {{ill|lt=torii|Q234731|qid=Q234731|1=Torii}} at the {{ill|lt=approach|Q667783|qid=Q667783|1=Sandō}} entrance is inscribed “Miminashi-yama.”
*There is a {{ill|lt=sangaku|Q2569069|qid=Q2569069|1=Sangaku}} dedicated in {{ill|lt=1854|Q7670|qid=Q7670|1=1854}} (Ansei 1) bearing a {{ill|lt=wasan|Q1735738|qid=Q1735738|1=Japanese mathematics}} problem and solution.

